    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>Linked Alarm Tampa Bay is dedicated to safeguarding your property with cutting-edge fire alarm systems, security cameras, access control, and IT solutions. As a trusted local provider, we prioritize life safety and reliable protection for both residential and commercial clients. Our team of factory-trained, NICET-certified technicians is committed to delivering honest, dependable, and rapid service tailored to meet your unique needs.</p>
        <p>We work with leading brands such as Alarm.com, Qolsys, Honeywell, DSC, Potter, Silent Knight, and Fire-Lite to deliver high-quality installations and maintenance. Our goal is to build lasting relationships with builders, property managers, homeowners, and renters through professional, customer-focused solutions.</p>
        <p>Why Choose Us? We stand out through our commitment to honesty, quality, and local expertise. With nationally recognized certifications and factory training, we ensure every project meets industry standards while offering unbeatable customer support. No job is too big or too small for our team. We guarantee satisfaction by providing comprehensive solutions from design and installation to maintenance and monitoring.</p>
    </section>
    <section id="inspections">
        <h2>Inspections</h2>
        <p>Our NFPA 72-compliant fire alarm inspections cover residential and commercial properties. We perform comprehensive testing of fire alarm panels, smoke detectors, manual pull stations, horn strobes, wiring, battery life, and more. Our skilled technicians ensure that your fire protection systems are fully operational, safe, and compliant with local codes.</p>
        <p>We provide thorough inspection reports and upload results to the city’s compliance portal when required. Our inspection services include visual and functional checks, system diagnostics, and recommendations for upgrades or maintenance. We proudly offer competitive rates and promise to beat competitors’ inspection prices by at least 10% when proof of equal service is provided.</p>
    </section>
    <section id="service">
        <h2>Service</h2>
        <p>We provide full maintenance and repair services for fire alarm systems, security cameras, access control systems, and IT infrastructure. Our team handles everything from regular system checks to emergency repairs, ensuring your safety and peace of mind.</p>
        <p>Our service offerings include diagnostics, troubleshooting, battery replacements, software updates, and system performance evaluations. We understand that downtime can compromise safety, so we respond rapidly to service calls and work diligently to restore system functionality.</p>
        <p>Whether you need routine maintenance or a full system overhaul, Linked Alarm Tampa Bay is your go-to provider for dependable and efficient service. We keep your systems in top shape to maintain consistent protection.</p>
    </section>
    <section id="installation">
        <h2>Installation</h2>
        <p>Our installation services are designed to provide reliable and customized fire alarm, security, and IT solutions. We assess your property’s needs and design an optimal system layout to maximize safety and efficiency. Our installation team handles new systems, upgrades, and integrations, always adhering to industry standards.</p>
        <p>We specialize in systems from top brands like Potter, Silent Knight, Fire-Lite, Alarm.com, Qolsys, Honeywell, and DSC. Our technicians ensure every installation is professionally executed, fully tested, and ready for operation. From residential homes to large commercial facilities, we deliver tailored solutions that meet your protection needs.</p>
    </section>
